StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetNwaProspectIDFromPhysicalIST]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@IstID uniqueiden..er
AS BEGIN
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT NwaID, ProspectID FROM USMC.Prospect WHERE ProspectID = ( SELECT ProspectID FROM USMC.ProspectPhysicalIst WHERE ID = @IstID )
END
